OL,3,CElon Musk could become world's first
OL,4,Ctrillionaire thanks to Tesla share deal
OL,6,FThe world's richest man, Elon Musk,
OL,7,Fcould become the world's first
OL,8,Ftrillionaire due to Tesla shareholders.
OL,10,FMusk won a shareholder vote that could
OL,11,Fsee him receive Tesla shares worth $1
OL,12,Ftrillion (#762 billion) if he meets
OL,13,Fcertain performance targets over the
OL,14,Fnext decade.
