OL,3,CElon Musk could become world's first
OL,4,Ctrillionaire thanks to Tesla share deal
OL,6,FThe decision follows weeks of debate
OL,7,Fover his management record at the
OL,8,Felectric car maker and whether anyone
OL,9,Fshould receive such an extraordinary
OL,10,Fpay package, sparking reactions from
OL,11,Finvestors, pension funds and even the
OL,12,Fpope.
OL,14,FIn the end, more than 75% of
OL,15,Fshareholders backed the plan during
OL,16,Fthe company's annual meeting in
OL,17,FAustin, Texas.
