OL,3,CElon Musk could become world's first
OL,4,Ctrillionaire thanks to Tesla share deal
OL,6,F"Fantastic group of shareholders,"
OL,7,FMusk said after the final vote was
OL,8,Ftallied. "Hang on to your Tesla
OL,9,Fstock," he added.
OL,11,FThe vote marks a major victory for
OL,12,FMusk, showing that investors still
OL,13,Fhave faith in him despite Tesla's
OL,14,Frecent struggles with falling sales,
OL,15,Fshrinking market share and declining
OL,16,Fprofits, problems many blame partly on
OL,17,FMusk himself.
