OL,6,FEven so, many investors continue to
OL,7,Fview Musk as a visionary capable of
OL,8,Fextraordinary comebacks, recalling how
OL,9,Fhe rescued Tesla from the brink of
OL,10,Fbankruptcy six years ago and turned it
OL,11,Finto one of the world's most valuable
OL,12,Fcompanies.
OL,14,FThe vote paves the way for Musk to
OL,15,Fbecome the world's first trillionaire,
OL,16,Fgranting him new Tesla shares if he
OL,17,Fmeets a series of ambitious targets.
