OL,3,CElon Musk could become world's first
OL,4,Ctrillionaire thanks to Tesla share deal
OL,6,FThe company's board has tied his pay
OL,7,Fto several ambitious financial and
OL,8,Foperational targets that would see
OL,9,FTesla's market value rise nearly
OL,10,Fsixfold, including increasing the
OL,11,Fvalue of the company on the stock
OL,12,Fmarket nearly six times its current
OL,13,Flevel.
OL,15,FMusk also has to deliver the
OL,16,Fproduction of 20 million Tesla
OL,17,Felectric vehicles over the next decade
OL,18,Fdespite there being stiff competition
OL,19,Fin the market, and the deployment of
OL,20,Fone million humanoid robots - a "robot
OL,21,Farmy" as Musk calls it.
