OL,4,Ctrillionaire thanks to Tesla share deal
OL,6,FHis win came despite opposition from
OL,7,Fmajor investors, including CalPERS,
OL,8,Fthe largest US public pension fund,
OL,9,Fand Norway's sovereign wealth fund.
OL,11,FCorporate watchdogs Institutional
OL,12,FShareholder Services and Glass Lewis
OL,13,Falso criticised the deal, prompting
OL,14,FMusk to label them "corporate
OL,15,Fterrorists" at a recent investor
OL,16,Fmeeting.
OL,18,FCritics argue the board of directors
OL,19,Fis too loyal to Musk and that his
OL,20,Frecent behaviour has been too reckless
OL,21,Fto justify such a reward.
